\id GEN 
\rem \xt at book level
\mt1 GENESIS
\ip Bible a lekhabu hmasak chem achang angkan, Genesis ahin thil inṭan poimaw tamka a loi infûnkhawm. Changrochu, Pathian tlanna riruatna hi thil inṭan poimaw chem chu achang. Bung \xt 1-2\xt* Pathianin rinênga ân lalnaram a tungding. Ani chun ama angka chiain manmasi chu a siama, ama thlengin rinêng chunga thû a nei theina dingin. Bung \xt 3\xt* achun, Adam nih Evi manmasi hmasakhei chun Pathian hmêlma Setan achu an zui. Anni chun a siampu doiin an hela, an sualna chu manmasi chithla kapai hniang achun ân dar ta a, tuarna nânsatak chu a hong râ suak ta a. Bung \xt 4-11\xt* achun sualna leia tiana boiralnahei nih khovêl pumpui tui lian a târlang. 